{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381040/extras/image.png?t=1737392374\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>One Puck, One Net; One Goal.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">LAW 56 takes players to the future of professional hockey, where player safety is no longer a concern. Rules have changed to create the fastest and most hard hitting experience possible. The arenas look closer to skate parks. There is only one net (protected by a robot). You can throw rockets at opponents. And up to 4 teams can battle it out at once to score the most goals, or deliver the biggest hits.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players use their expanded movement capabilities to navigate arenas, collect the puck, and fire it past the goalie to score the most goals, battering into their opponents along the way to gain an advantage. Arenas are designed to facilitate the players movement capabilities with boost pads, grind rails, and wall runs opportunities, to create a flowing and fluid feel to the movement. Arenas are peppered with item spawns for an element of unpredictability and to add to the party game feel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>DEMO Includes:</u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Free For All game mode for up to 4 players\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Two hockey arenas</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Training Arena for players to learn the ropes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">All 8 Teams to choose from</p></li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3381040?t=1737392374","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381040/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1737392374","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381040/da39173e8933655de4f49e8da8780d7e40315012/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737392374","capsule_imagev5"